name: Created On Purpose for God's Purpose
description: The Christian life is supposed to be vibrant and full of meaning, but more often than not, many Christians, young and old, find themselves wondering what life is about and if there is a divine plan after all. Created on Purpose for God’s Purpose was born out of one such Christian’s purpose journey and explains what she discovered along the way. The result is eight practical and insightful biblical principles for the searching person to follow if they want to fulfill God’s purpose for their lives.

name: 2014 Thankful Calendar
description: This brightly colored calendar will inspire you daily to be thankful. It features 12 attributes of God that each person continually benefits from; consequently, it is worthwhile to simply stop for a moment each day and than God for all He has done.
